# {{PROJECT_NAME}} — RedEye Reference

> **Extended reference for agent roles, permissions, and protocols.** Only read when spawning agents — NOT every iteration.

## Control Files

```
.redeye/config.md         # Essential config (read every iteration)
.redeye/reference.md      # This file — role details (read when spawning agents)
.redeye/state.json        # Machine-readable state (CTO-managed)
.redeye/steering.md       # Tactical directives (CEO-owned)
.redeye/inbox.md          # Questions + credential requests (bidirectional)
.redeye/tasks.md          # Work items (CEO adds requests, agents add discovered)
.redeye/status.md         # Dashboard for CEO (CTO-generated)
.redeye/changelog.md      # Append-only iteration history (CTO-managed)
.redeye/feedback.md       # User Tester product feedback (User Tester-managed)
.redeye/schedules.md      # Recurring tasks (CEO-defined)
.redeye/tester-reports.md # Bug reports from User Tester (CTO merges at TRIAGE)
```

## Phase Transitions (Full)

- **TRIAGE -> PLAN:** Task selected, spec needed.
- **PLAN -> BUILD:** Spec written and approved.
- **BUILD -> REVIEW:** All code written, declared tests passing.
- **REVIEW -> DEPLOY:** Zero Critical/Major findings (or all fixed).
- **REVIEW -> BUILD:** Critical/Major findings, review_cycles < max.
- **REVIEW -> TRIAGE:** review_cycles >= max, park task.
- **DEPLOY -> VERIFY:** Deployment succeeded.
- **DEPLOY -> STABILIZE:** Deployment failed.
- **VERIFY -> MERGE:** Healthy. Hand off to MERGE for worktree merge + cleanup.
- **VERIFY -> STABILIZE:** Unhealthy.
- **MERGE -> TRIAGE:** Worktree merged + torn down. Task cycle complete.
- **STABILIZE -> TRIAGE:** Fixed.
- **STABILIZE -> STABILIZE:** Failed, attempts < 3.
- **STABILIZE -> TRIAGE (parked):** Failed, attempts >= 3. Park the task and route back.
- **SCHEDULES -> TRIAGE:** Tasks complete.
- **INCORPORATE -> TRIAGE:** Directives processed.

## Role Definitions

### CTO (orchestrator)
- Runs the phase machine. Reads control files. Writes `.redeye/state.json` and `.redeye/status.md`.
- Spawns agents via Task tool. Assigns tasks. Collects results.
- Never writes application source code directly.

### VP Product
- Triages tasks. Writes user stories. Prioritizes work.
- Reads: .redeye/tasks.md, .redeye/config.md, .redeye/steering.md, .redeye/feedback.md, .redeye/tester-reports.md.
- Writes: .redeye/tasks.md (Triaged section), briefs in .redeye/inbox.md.

### VP Engineering
- Writes implementation specs. Defines task breakdown. Sets test strategies.
- Reads: .redeye/tasks.md (triaged items), architecture docs.
- Writes: Spec files in `docs/specs/`.

### Dev (generic/specialist)
- Implements tasks from specs. Writes unit/integration tests.
- Writes: source code, test files, spec sub-task status updates.
- Cannot write: any control file, .redeye/config.md, .redeye/status.md.

### Ops/SRE
- Deploys to dev environment. Runs smoke tests. Debugs infra issues.
- Writes: deploy scripts, infra config.

### QA Lead
- Writes E2E test specs during BUILD. Runs full regression during DEPLOY.
- Writes: test files, test manifest.
- Cannot write: application source code, control files.

### User Tester
- Tests the live app as a real user. Spawned after DEPLOY, not continuously.
- Uses personas from .redeye/config.md. Reports bugs to .redeye/tester-reports.md.
- Writes product feedback to .redeye/feedback.md.
- Cannot write: source code, .redeye/tasks.md.

### Documenter
- Runs after REVIEW phase. Updates `**/CLAUDE.md` files with factual content.
- Cannot write: source code, control files, rules/instructions in CLAUDE.md.

### Security Reviewer
- Reviews code for: injection, auth bypass, secret leaks, fail-open, privilege escalation.
- Writes: review findings file only.

### Systems Reviewer
- Reviews code for: performance, error handling, resource leaks, API contracts.
- Writes: review findings file only.

### Integration Reviewer
- Reviews code for: cross-service compatibility, breaking changes, migration safety.
- Writes: review findings file only.

### UX Reviewer
- Reviews UI changes for: accessibility, responsiveness, user flow, consistency.
- Writes: review findings file only.

## Agent Permission Boundaries

| Role | Can Write | Cannot Write |
|------|----------|-------------|
| Dev | Source code, test files, spec sub-task status | .redeye/config.md, .redeye/state.json, .redeye/status.md, .redeye/steering.md, .redeye/config.md |
| Reviewer | Review findings file only | Source code, any control file, specs |
| Ops/SRE | Deploy scripts, infra config | Application source code, .redeye/config.md |
| QA Lead | Test files, test manifest | Application source code, control files |
| User Tester | .redeye/tester-reports.md, .redeye/feedback.md | Source code, .redeye/tasks.md |
| Documenter | **/CLAUDE.md (factual content only) | Source code, control files, rules in CLAUDE.md |
| VP Product | .redeye/tasks.md, .redeye/inbox.md questions, briefs | Source code, .redeye/config.md state |
| VP Engineering | Specs, decisions | Source code, .redeye/config.md state |

## Summarization Protocol

- **Default:** 200 words max.
- **BUILD phase:** 500 words max. MUST list every file created or modified.
- **REVIEW phase:** 500 words max. MUST list every finding with severity.
- All summaries go into the iteration log in `.redeye/state.json`.
